comment.author: 55198937@N05
comment._content: Built by the Sydney Harbour Trust in Argyle Street in 1905, and No 6 (Duggan's) remodelled to this design shortly thereafter (1906?) - and c1914 the lovely semi-circular bay window was bricked up!.. See Dept Housing Conservation management review Pages 118 & 119 for a history of this building and earlier photo : www.housing.nsw.gov.au/NR/rdonlyres/B4548FEF-B16F-4B09-AE...
